The paper discusses active learning strategies for object classification, which is a common problem in machine learning and computer vision. The proposed algorithm involves constructing a graph and evaluating subqueries hierarchically, which suggests a focus on graph-based methods and optimization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
